17
00:03:22,590 --> 00:03:24,150
How did he become like this?

18
00:03:24,310 --> 00:03:25,710
What's going on?

19
00:03:26,870 --> 00:03:28,230
A person who looks like you

20
00:03:28,230 --> 00:03:29,670
