155
00:12:56,190 --> 00:12:57,100
It's my business.

156
00:12:57,510 --> 00:12:58,670
Don't worry about it.

157
00:12:59,350 --> 00:13:00,350
You'd better handle

158
00:13:00,350 --> 00:13:01,990
